OL,5,FIndeed, ITV News has seen evidence of
OL,6,Fseveral CBD companies selling flower
OL,7,Fwithin the UK.
OL,9,FMany suppliers are calling on the
OL,10,Fgovernment to update the law around
OL,11,FCBD products, so that legality is
OL,12,Fbased on psychoactive substances -
OL,13,Frather than the material itself.
OL,15,F"So what the EU law states is that any
OL,16,Fflower with less than 0.2% THC is a
OL,17,FCBD flower and, therefore, legal,"
OL,18,FGeorge said.
