OL,3,CDoes the UK's law on CBD need updating?
OL,5,FWhen we put this to the Home Office,
OL,6,Fthe government did suggest more
OL,7,Fclarity is needed, a spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "CBD, as an isolated substance,
OL,9,Fis not a controlled drug. We will be
OL,10,Fproviding greater clarity for
OL,11,Fresponsible suppliers by introducing
OL,12,Fdefined limits on the controlled drug
OL,13,Fcontent of consumer CBD products".
